OL,3,CElectrical fire in garden shed damages
OL,4,Cfive homes in village
OL,6,FFive homes have been damaged in
OL,7,FHeadley, near Bordon, after a fire
OL,8,Fbroke out in a garden shed.
OL,10,FCrews from Hampshire and Isle of Wight
OL,11,FFire and Rescue Service were called to
OL,12,FBirch Road at around 4pm on Saturday
OL,13,Fafternoon.
OL,15,FThis included firefighters from Alton,
OL,16,FBordon, Petersfield, Rushmoor and St
OL,17,FMary's, plus crews from Surrey Fire
OL,18,Fand Rescue Service.
OL,20,FCrews spent several hours bringing the
OL,21,Fincident under control.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
