OL,3,CElectrical fire in garden shed damages
OL,4,Cfive homes in village
OL,6,FThe fire, which originated in a
OL,7,Fgarden, quickly spread to neighbouring
OL,8,Fproperties and nearby cars.
OL,10,FNobody was injured but two dogs were
OL,11,Frescued from a house and given oxygen
OL,12,Ftherapy by firefighters, before being
OL,13,Ftaken to a vet.
OL,15,FThe cause of the fire is thought to be
OL,16,Fdue to an electrical fault.
